Chris and James dip Genevieve's front wheel in the Atlantic at Portsmouth, NH



I don&rsquo;t yet feel ready to reflect on the experiences of the past 7 weeks, but I do want to say a few heartfelt thank yous:

To the America By Bicycle staff for shepherding us across this vast continent
To Genevieve for being such a trusty and willing mount
To James and Alastair for being the most brilliant pilots and gentleman&rsquo;s gentlemen I could imagine
