James and Chris at the border crossing from Wisconsin into Michigan (at Ludington)



It really is starting to feel as though we have broken the back of this journey now, although with 2,719 miles done, we still have 934 miles to go. And that remaining 934 miles is still slightly longer than the standard Lands End to John o&rsquo;Groats End To End ride across the UK.
