For the first time since Day 0 it actually rained during today&rsquo;s ride for 30 minutes or so. We did get drenched but I made a conscious decision not to wear a rain jacket to avoid that delightful boil in the bag effect brought on by wearing waterproof garments on a hot and humid day.
